import React from 'react'
// import axios from 'axios'
import { BrowserRouter, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import About from './components/common/About'
import Blog from './components/common/Blog'
import Courses from './components/common/Courses'
import Home from './components/common/Home'
import Leaderboards from './components/common/Leaderboards'
import Members from './components/common/Members'
import Records from './components/common/Records'
import Tours from './components/common/Tours'

function App() {


  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path="/" component={Home} />
        {/* <Route path="/movies/new" component={MovieNew}/>
        <Route path="/movies/:id" component={MovieShow} /> */}
        <Route path="/about" component={About} />
        <Route path="/members" component={Members} />
        <Route path="/tours" component={Tours} />
        <Route path="/leaderboards" component={Leaderboards} />
        <Route path="/records" component={Records} />
        <Route path="/courses" component={Courses} />
        <Route path="/blog" component={Blog} />
        <Route path="/contact" component={Members} />
      </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )


}

export default App
